---
title: Venison Steak & Caramelised Onion Panini with Gravy Sauce & Fries
description: A steak sandwich is on everyone’s mind tonight, but don’t settle for any old one. Jazz it up with a tender venison steak, with sweet caramelised onion and salad. Even the panini is getting an upgrade by toasting it with a layer of smoked Cheddar. Serve with a classic fries and gravy combo and you’ve got one good looking, totally delicious panini!
